title: Introduction to Topology and Modern Analysis [DjVu]
description:
Introduction to Topology and Modern Analysis (1963)
by George F. Simmons


This material is intended to contribute to a wider appreciation of the mathematical words "continuity and linearity".

The book's purpose is to illuminate the meanings of these words and their relation to each other.
